      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #333; font-size: 22px;">ğŸ’¡ Sample Topic Ideas</h3>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px;">
        <div style="padding: 12px; background: #e7f3ff; border-radius: 6px; color: #0056b3; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">ğŸ Python for Data Science</div>
        <div style="padding: 12px; background: #fff3cd; border-radius: 6px; color: #856404; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">âš›ï¸ React Hooks Tutorial</div>
        <div style="padding: 12px; background: #d4edda; border-radius: 6px; color: #155724; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">ğŸ³ Docker Best Practices</div>
