        <div style="padding: 12px; background: #d1ecf1; border-radius: 6px; color: #0c5460; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">ğŸš€ Node.js Performance</div>
        <div style="padding: 12px; background: #e2e3e5; border-radius: 6px; color: #383d41; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">ğŸ“Š SQL Optimization</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    

    
    <!-- Link to Blog -->
